72
00:07:38.750 --> 00:07:43.504
<i>Dear passengers. this U5 service
to Hönow is ready to depart...</i>

73
00:07:43.505 --> 00:07:44.755
Sam?

74
00:07:44.756 --> 00:07:45.757
I...

75
