Exactly what you are</i>

81
00:08:48.862 --> 00:08:51.614
{\an8}<i>Just keep your head held high</i>

82
00:08:51.615 --> 00:08:54.409
{\an8}<i>Kiss your fist. and touch the sky</i>

83
00:08:54.993 --> 00:08:59.581
{\an8}<i>Too late to keep the world from dying</i>

84
00:09:00.791 --> 00:09:02.543
{\an8}<i>One day</i>

85
00:09:03.043 --> 00:09:04.961
{\an8}<i>Whoo</i>

86
00:09:04.962 --> 00:09:06.922
{\an8}<i>We'll all be there</i>

87
00:09:08.715 --> 00:09:11.510
{\an8}<i>Yeah. yeah. yeah
Yeah. yeah. yeah</i>

88
00:09:35.576 --> 00:09:39.453
We can't turn the power on
while they are still down there.

89
00:09:39.454 --> 00:09:40.873
You know that!

90
00:09:41.707 --> 00:09:43.499
We need to get the network back up.

91
00:09:43.500 --> 00:09:44.792
Right now.

92
00:09:44.793 --> 00:09:47.671
<i>Yes. yes. I get it.
I think I see them coming now...</i>

93
00:09:49.423 --> 00:09:51.884
Get a move on. We need to leave.

94
00:10:07.524 --> 00:10:09.776
Confirming all personnel are out.

95
00:10:10.569 --> 00:10:11.778
Ah. great!

96
00:10:12.321 --> 00:10:13.322
Thank you very much.

97
